Kubernetes resource icons
--------------------------
Files: web/src/assets/k8s/*.svg

The SVG icons used in the web UI to represent Kubernetes resource kinds
(Pod, Deployment, Service, ConfigMap, Secret, ...) are the official
Kubernetes resource icons, vendored from the kubernetes/community
repository (icons/svg, unlabeled variants):

    https://github.com/kubernetes/community/tree/master/icons

